dance at z \\gsim 4 and with the\nlarge optical depth to reionization measured by the Wilkinson Microwave\nAnisotropy Probe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2005 06:53:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 May 2005 17:35:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 26 Nov 2005 06:46:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
